<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f7fb;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    code {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    ul {
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>Server API đang chạy thành công.</p>
    <p>Test nhanh các endpoint:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>POST /api/v1/auth/login</code></li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/auth/me</code> (Bearer token)</li>
      <li><code>POST /api/v1/auth/change-password</code> (Bearer token)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
